Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and ready the next blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It will take time to recharge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, send out our mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ericht!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Ericht!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ericht!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.93,0:00:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suletta!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suletta!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Suletta!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Guel... everyone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suletta! Do you read me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suletta!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty gruesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What... happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Spread of information\Nthermological entropy confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It has reached the level\Nwhere her body is under threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Ericht?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Till and the others\Nare checking things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't get up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ericht is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That blast just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably an interplanetary laser\Ntransmission system at high output.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, it will take time\Nto recharge for the next blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Suletta and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we'd better blow this joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nika! Chuchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,President Miorine... it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attention Headquarters!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Any further attacks\Nare in violation of law!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,After violating the principles\Nof peace between the fronts,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the Benerit Group has no leg to stand on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As defenders of the fronts,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the Space Assembly League\Nis acting with cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How was Ms. Ericht?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't respond...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The drive systems are all damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be why.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us ten minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll shift Aerial's\Npropulsion controls to the Calibarn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We may not be as good as Nika,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but we've spent plenty of time\Nworking on Aerial too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't forgiven you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lauda?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't come home with my brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll forgive that even less.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll head straight there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Space Assembly League?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}President Jeturk, please return\Nto Quiet Zero immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Focus on your duties.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A wireless optical transmission?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no orders to engage them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you want to get caught\Nin that thing's line of fire?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A laser transmission system?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be\Nan infrastructure front,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,providing power to Lagrange 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd heard rumors that\Nit might be co-opted for military use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it one more time.\NHand over Aerial.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, your lives will end here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta cares about you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll come without being told...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Along with Aerial.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suletta...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine, Ms. Nika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Suletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you reconnect the continuity chord,\NEri will reawaken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please connect Eri to Quiet Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,hand Ericht to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Suletta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom's body will be paralyzed soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've managed to put on a good act,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but my legs have been useless for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Data storm infection?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eri will gain a world woven by GUND,\Nand her freedom as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us can find happiness\Nin their respective places of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you care about Eri,\Nyou can move forward too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Ericht doesn't want\Nto lose you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,who needs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this Quiet Zero thing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Suletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't handle it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... in trouble again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr... Elan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The organoid archive of\Nthe enhanced humans is integrated here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that means I'm like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Elan, it was my fault that you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't regret dueling with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that I couldn't meet you like I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin, Suletta Mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The data storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Ericht!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Answer me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so silly, Suletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can choose for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a place where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet... this is what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a greedy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much I want to do
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with Mom and all of you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it Quiet Zero?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No signs of attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Miorine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quiet Zero is being targeted again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone, please flee!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You too, Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not another inch--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to rid the League\Nof their motives, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lagrange 4!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And all citizens in the region!\NCan you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:17.73,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the President of the Benerit Group...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose voice is that? Cut it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:19.25,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Miorine Rembran.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Benerit Group has just submitted\Nits papers of dissolution and liquidation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As was the case with Grassley,\Nall of the group's assets{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will be sold to or merged with\NEarthian corporations,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}per mutual agreement.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.03,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In addition...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dissolution?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:42.03,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we've received evidence that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.10,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the League's High Council colluded\Nwith Grassley Defense Systems...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How? When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and was complicit\Nin the recent attacks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The evidence was received, along with\NShaddiq Zenelli's written confession,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and we promise to make it public!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As always...\NI could never compete with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alea iacta est.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this at his request?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Miorine... Rembran!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What about our assets?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she sold every last bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're resigning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say\NI've been headhunted...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown tired of being\Non the Peil Grade's leash, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Buh-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That weapon of mass destruction\Nstill stands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy recharge is still underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The laser transmission system\Nhas been overridden.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The firing phase has been shut down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She actually exceeded... score eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suletta is the only one\Ncapable of raising Eri's score.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:13:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Elnora...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come home to the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nadeem? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You made us all proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't it still too early\Nfor her to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done enough, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost Nadeem,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Cardo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lose Eri too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud of you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You called everyone here from Aerial,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For Ericht's sake,\Nyou chose the future over revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if everyone objects,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,if they say that it's wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,your choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,has my support.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What you... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay with Suletta from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With you too, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suletta...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Permet is breaking apart\Nat the particle level.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please evacuate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms... Miorine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.70,OS - TNR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,1}3 years later
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How was the certification test?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect nothing less\Nfrom our ace mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to balance\Nwork and school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's Chuchu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You changed the specs without asking!\NYou turdish Spacian geek--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That qualifies as verbal harassment...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She could have at least\Nwritten the location...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:19:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Plant Quetta was one thing,\Nbut Quiet Zero was not your crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd decided on my own, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving for Quinharbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Making up for things\Nwill be hard for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The trial is about to commence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Miorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd listen to\Nyour sister-in-law's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure remind me of your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be a tester for GUND-ARM Inc.\Nstarting next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be at Petra's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't rely on my big brother forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ceres...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful that\Nyou'd bring me new business, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped keep Asticassia open, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:20:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I helped you find new jobs\Nfor your employees.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now it's your turn to listen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who drew up the documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The division of profits\Nseems awfully stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you want to rebuild\Nyour company, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,President Jeturk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Benerit Group assets we distributed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They'll just be scooped up by space again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if it was the right move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There are as many "right moves"\Nas there are individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We all make mistakes at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have to keep doing what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to make a school here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gradually regained\Ncontrol of my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and my mom likes it here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what's so great\Nabout living in the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't get how you even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I do, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the one who transferred us\Nfrom Aerial that day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was definitely you, Suletta.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something that only you could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:33.85,OS - TNR,,0,0,15,,{\an8\fad(60,800)\fs24}Episode 24
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.94,0:23:52.25,OS,Caption,32,20,15,,{\an7}Illustration: mogmog
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.94,0:23:52.25,OS,Caption,20,32,15,,{\an3}Thank you very much for watching the show until the end!
